WEBVTT

00:08:27.217 --> 00:08:31.105
by adhering to these
research-backed principles.

00:08:31.607 --> 00:08:34.905
One: report all the facts

00:08:34.929 --> 00:08:36.830
on the mindset,

00:08:36.854 --> 00:08:38.192
demographics

00:08:38.216 --> 00:08:42.190
and motivational profile
of these shooters,

00:08:42.214 --> 00:08:46.390
but minimize their names and images,

00:08:46.414 --> 00:08:47.908
unless they're at large.

00:08:48.789 --> 00:08:53.881
Two: limit the use of the shooter's name

00:08:53.905 --> 00:08:55.368
to once per piece,

00:08:55.392 --> 00:08:57.157
never in the headlines

00:08:57.181 --> 00:09:00.359
and no pictures in prominent locations.